metadata.group_name: Mind Over Matter: Decluttering Support Group

text: The 'Mind Over Matter: Decluttering Support Group' runs at the Stevenage Wellbeing Centre centre on Wednesdays at 1:00pm (from 9th April 2025). It runs for 12 weeks. Registration is required. About the group: A 12-week support group helping people address clutter through practical and emotional strategies in a non-judgemental environment. Topics covered include: Understanding causes and triggers of clutter; Strategies for decluttering and organising your space; Overcoming emotional attachment to items; Self-care, setbacks, and sustaining progress. This group is suitable for: Anyone feeling overwhelmed by belongings or struggling to maintain an organised space.
